[[span class="bigtext"]]##42425a|__CONTAINMENT PROCEDURES:__## [[/span]] The corpse of SCP-6651 is to be kept inside SCP-6651-1.

Essophysical entities tied with known concepts may not enter the 50m radius area of SCP-6651.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]][[span class="bigtext"]]//essophysics// (n).:[[/span]] The study of embodiments, the physical manifestation of ideas within the noosphere.[[/span]]

[[span class="old"]][[span class="fae"]]err @[DATA UNCOMPREHENSIBLE][[/span]] is to be stationed around SCP-6651-1. If SCP-6651 attempts to breach SCP-6651-1, it is to be neutralized.[[/span]][[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Various pieces of archived data have been kept in the document due to their importance in understanding the following anomaly, these have been colored gray to differentiate them from up-to-date information. @@     @@[[span class="bigtext"]]##fff36d|--RAISA##[[/span]][[/span]]
