[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Can anyone read this? Is there anyone online?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Hello? What's happening, [[span class="fae"]]@Aleksander T.[[/span]]?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Oh my god, can you hear me?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Yeah? Why, what's up?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Like two weeks ago, I- had to terminate an anomaly, SCP-6651, and at first I thought that everyone was playing a prank on me but now.. I- I don't know, there must have been a side effect.[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## I see, well, let me just see something, alright? **[# @Site Command]** Can we get some researchers on this?

**##gray|Site Command:##** On what, Ra?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Command? Command! Can you read me, command?![[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## This guy, Aleksander, some antimemetic side-effects from neutralizing an anomaly, he says.

**##gray|Site Command:##** Yeah sure, just send his current location and chat ID.

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## On it.

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## He is currently in [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/secure-facility-dossier-site-120 Level 4], cannot specify which room. As for the chat ID, [[span class="fae"]]Aleksander_T::#487207413[[/span]].

**##gray|Site Command:##** As for the chat ID...?

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Already sent it?

**##gray|Site Command:##** Nothing appears on my end, I'm going to try reconnect.

[[span class="old"]]<<**[# @Site Command]** has left the channel.[[/span]]

----

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Alright, [[span class="fae"]]@Aleksander T.[[/span]] Since Command hasn't relogged, I've conducted a Site-Wide scan on my own, and...

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: I don't want to know, I just need to talk with someone, I've been alone for the past two weeks, I think, Ra. Please.[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Alright, then do you want to know how my day has been or...?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Anything.[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Well I've been good, sorting through files, pulling other files up... Nothing too exciting today, well, other than chatting with a potential anomaly through the site's chatroom :)

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## I guess I know the answer but what about you?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: I'm... better now. Thank you, Ra.[[/span]]
