**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Hey! [[span class="fae"]]@Aleksander T.[[/span]] Have you heard the news?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: News? No, what's happened?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Have you not heard anything about [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6500 The Impasse]? Really?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Well I've heard about it, but what's happened, why are there more news about it?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## The Foundation is going to be dissolved, and merge with other organizations to create VANGUARD. That's basically the news. What do you think about it?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Well, it definitely seems like a smart choice, that's for sure...[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Nothing //else// to say?

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: It's a shame I can't work for the Foundation anymore, would like to see what happens from the inside, I can say that.[[/span]]

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: What will happen to you, though?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## I'm sure [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6172 I'll keep busy], worst comes of it, I could talk with you.

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: That would be good for both of us, don't you think?[[/span]]

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Yep.

**##b69126|Ra.aic:**## Hey Alex, I need to get some work done, I'll be back in a bit.

[[span class="fae"]]Aleksander T.: Alright, see you when you're done, then.[[/span]]

